
1. ## Install docker in k8s node
sudo yum update
sudo yum install docker

2. ## Install docker in jenkins
sudo apt install docker.io


3. ## mount volume /var/run/docker.sock and make privileged


4. # setup docker registry


5. # Create docker registry secret to pull images



Install plugin  : Generic Webhook Trigger

Webhook  : http://Jenkins_URL/github-webhook/
www urlencoded 
Jenkins : GitHub hook trigger for GITScm polling




kubectl create secret docker-registry docker-credentials \ 
    --docker-username=<username>  \
    --docker-password=<password> \
    --docker-email=<email-address>